<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800">
    <header class="bg-navy text-white py-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Christ Connect</h1>
            <p class="text-lg">Privacy Policy</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Privacy Policy for Christ Connect</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Last Updated: March 31, 2025</p>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Introduction</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">Welcome to Christ Connect, an all-in-one application designed specifically for Christ University students. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use our application. By using Christ Connect, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Information We Collect</h3>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">1. Account Information</h4>
                    <p>When you sign up for Christ Connect using Google Sign-In, we collect basic account information such as your name, email address, and profile picture associated with your Google account.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">2. Google Classroom Data</h4>
                    <p class="mb-2">With your permission, we access:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-2">
                        <li>Your enrolled courses (read-only)</li>
                        <li>Classroom announcements (read-only)</li>
                        <li>Course materials (read-only)</li>
                        <li>Your coursework and assignments (read-only)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">3. Email Data</h4>
                    <p class="mb-2">With your permission, we access:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-2">
                        <li>Your Gmail messages (read-only)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">4. User-Generated Content</h4>
                    <p class="mb-2">We collect information you provide when you:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-2">
                        <li>Set notification reminders</li>
                        <li>Create announcements (for Class Representatives)</li>
                        <li>Edit your profile details</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">5. Usage Information</h4>
                    <p class="mb-2">We collect information about how you use our app, including:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-2">
                        <li>Features you access</li>
                        <li>Time spent on different sections</li>
                        <li>App performance data</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h3>
                <p class="mb-2">We use your information to:</p>
                <ul class="mb-4">
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Provide Core App Functionality:</span> Display your classroom announcements, coursework, deadlines, and emails.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Organize Content:</span> Categorize your emails and academic information for easier access.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Enable Notifications:</span> Send reminders based on your preferences.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Improve User Experience:</span> Analyze usage patterns to enhance app features and performance.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Technical Support:</span> Troubleshoot issues and provide customer support.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Communication:</span> Send important updates about the app.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Data Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
                <p class="mb-2">We do not sell your personal information to third parties. We may share your information in the following circumstances:</p>
                <ul class="mb-4">
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">With Your Consent:</span> When you explicitly allow us to share specific information.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Service Providers:</span> With third-party vendors who help us operate our app (e.g., hosting providers, analytics services).</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Legal Requirements:</span> When required by law, court order, or governmental regulation.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Educational Institution:</span> We may share aggregate, non-personal information with Christ University for educational purposes.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Data Storage and Security</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Your data is stored on secure servers and we regularly review our security practices to ensure the highest level of protection.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Your Rights and Choices</h3>
                <p class="mb-2">You have the right to:</p>
                <ul class="mb-4">
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Access Your Data:</span> Request a copy of the personal information we hold about you.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Correct Inaccuracies:</span> Update or correct your personal information.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Delete Your Account:</span> Request deletion of your account and associated data.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Modify Permissions:</span> Change your Google account permissions for our app at any time through your Google Account settings.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-medium">Notification Preferences:</span> Control what notifications you receive from the app.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Children's Privacy</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">Christ Connect is designed for university students and is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 18.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Contact Us</h3>
                <p class="mb-2">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
                <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-medium">Email:</span> 
                    <a href="mailto:kishan.kumar@mca.christuniversity.in" class="text-navy hover:underline">kishan.kumar@mca.christuniversity.in</a>, 
                    <a href="mailto:sagar.sharma@mca.christuniversity.in" class="text-navy hover:underline">sagar.sharma@mca.christuniversity.in</a>
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
